                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>St Louis</placeName>\n                <date>April 16/54</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Dear Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">I shall remit to<lb/> you by the end of this week my reasons<lb/>\n                for writing now is that I have spare time<lb/>\n                <sic>wheras</sic> in the week my time is so taken<lb/> up by labor that I avail\n                myself of the<lb/> present time, the following persons<lb/> in your list are not in\n                the city <persName>S. Keller</persName><lb/>\n                <persName>J H Cohen</persName>, <persName>A N Hart</persName> &amp; <persName>W St\n                    Johns</persName> of those<lb/> here the following refused to take the bible<lb/>\n                <persName>M. Abrahams</persName>. <persName>J Barnum</persName>\n                <persName>A Langsdorf</persName>\n                <persName>J Woolf</persName><lb/>\n                <persName>A L Kumell</persName>. <persName>L H Plahto</persName>\n                <persName>J Micathened</persName><lb/> to have them advertised in the Occident<lb/>\n                particularly as <persName>H Plahto</persName> gave me an order<lb/> for a set of\n                    <persName>Piza</persName> Books according to your<lb/> circular. I Received from\n                    <persName>Mr Lats</persName> their<lb/> Tiphillas<add>?</add> 1-250-1-2.75 &amp;\n                1,5.000 The 2.75 one<lb/> I sold at $3.00 I also sold the 2.50 one the other is<lb/>\n                much <sic>soild</sic> and will never bring the price you<lb/> will please inform me\n                    <sic>wether</sic> I shall return<lb/> it to <persName>Mr Lats</persName> a sett\n                is for 3.00 as I think<lb/> that is about as much as it will bring<lb/> it may fetch\n                50/cents more. I received <persName>Dias</persName> Letters<lb/> through the mail\n                also the four Hagodahs which<lb/> came very opportune I shall now give you</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p33x8459h/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
