                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>of my stewardship I sold to private persons<lb/> four copies of the bible 2 a 11.00\n                &amp; 2â€”8.00<lb/> besides several <persName>Dias</persName> Letters I had also\n                to<lb/> pay one Sharnas five pr cent on<lb/> one hundred and five dollars the\n                persons being<lb/> at a distance than in my neighborhood<lb/> I collect myself a\n                shall do it</p>\n            <table cols=\"4\" rows=\"11\">\n                <row>\n                    <cell><persName role=\"author\">H Myers</persName> Dr to <persName>I\n                            Leeser</persName></cell>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell><persName role=\"author\">H Myers</persName> Or</cell>\n                    <cell/>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>To <sic>ballance</sic> of Billâ€”</cell>\n                    <cell>50</cell>\n                    <cell>Freight &amp;c</cell>\n                    <cell>10.50</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>1 Bible <add>?</add></cell>\n                    <cell>9â€”</cell>\n                    <cell>5 pr cent 105</cell>\n                    <cell>5.25</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>1 Set <persName>Piza</persName> Books</cell>\n                    <cell>25â€”</cell>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell>$15.75</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>13 Bibles 8â€”</cell>\n                    <cell>104â€”</cell>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell>165.25</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>1â€”</cell>\n                    <cell>9â€”</cell>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell/>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>8 <persName>Dias</persName>\n                        <add>?</add></cell>\n                    <cell>6â€”</cell>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell/>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>1 Tephillim</cell>\n                    <cell>2 50</cell>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell/>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell>3â€”</cell>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell/>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell>159â€”</cell>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell/>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>2 Bibles 11-00</cell>\n                    <cell>18.100.</cell>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell/>\n                </row>\n            </table>\n            <p>from this $165.25 will be deducted Exchange &amp;<lb/> discount, you will please\n                charge<lb/> a <persName>J Lats</persName> with 1 <persName>Dias</persName> letters\n                you<lb/> will also send the occident to <persName>J. A Hart</persName><lb/> of this\n                city commencing if come with the<lb/> first number just out he his good\n                <add>?</add><lb/> I have now on hand 5 Bibles at $800<lb/> 1 at $9.00 2 at $11.00\n                &amp; 6 <persName>Dias</persName> Letter's<lb/> you may rely upon my using my<lb/>\n                <sic>axertions</sic> to affect sales it <sic>ocurrs</sic> to me</p>"
                  },
